snippet.title: Barbie Project Friendship™ | Announce Trailer | US | ESRB
snippet.description:
Barbie and Barbie team up! 🎀
Your kids can enter a world of creativity and imagination in Barbie Project Friendship™, available on October 25th 💖
More info coming soon 👀
